{"tid":1325499,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC分析: TVB、有線、Now 「反送中」抗議的細微差別背後","createTime":"2019-07-17T01:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T02:06:19.000Z","uid":70437,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb39fa0bcebd73ca1d88855891588b33928f0fb","tid":1325499,"uid":70437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"香港電視廣播有限公司（無線電視，TVB）是近期在反送中運動成為示威者針對的目標。在抗議現場，經常發生示威者包圍TVB記者及採訪車的情況。<br />\n<br />\n示威者認為，TVB的新聞報道不夠中立，並戲稱其為「CCTV-B」，諷刺其親官方的姿態。他們發起包圍TVB總部及其活動的行動，導致一些宣傳活動要被迫取消。<br />\n<br />\nTVB新聞部表示，公司一直堅持中肯客觀的報道，對有人阻撓其前線記者工作感到極度遺憾。<br />\nBBC中文採訪了TVB新聞部的員工，了解他們的工作，同時對比了TVB及其他兩家主要新聞台在報道《逃犯條例》修訂時的操作手法有何異同。<br />\n<br />\n 詳情自己入去睇 ：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49001797?SThisFB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49001797%3FSThisFB&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSYmB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=6a90a0a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49001797%3FSThisFB&h=45674149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49001797?SThisFB</a>"},{"pid":"50cf5a7c6b0a95acf130c5513c7c20af2e6e52cc","tid":1325499,"uid":52928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"仲話自己中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人無恥即無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc1dda0b0b0be40f1ff867eabbff500cab055ff","tid":1325499,"uid":116785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"寧願報道「中立」都要同錢作對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}